            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Hd1e108">Rubrica 4</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De lucri acquisitionis honestate consideranda</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
      ¶ De luc. acquisitionis honestate
      <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>consideranda. Rubrica. 4
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/> <ref>PSalmista. 36 psalamus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e125">De
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>uus est mo¬ 
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>/dicum iusto super diuitias peccato
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>rum multas.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>
                <ref>¶ Salomon in prouerbiis. c. 16.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e139">Melius est
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>parum cum iusticia quam multi fructus cum ini
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>quitate.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e148"> <ref>/ c. 17.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e150">Melior est bucella sicca cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>gaudio quam domus plena victimis cum iurgio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e156">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
                <ref>¶ Isocrates in exhortationibus. c. 2 ad fi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e160">Amplectere magis iustam penuriam quam in
        <lb ed="#V" n="27" break="no"/>iustas diuitias. hc enim iustitia diuitiis poti
        <lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>or. Neminem celeris lucrantem nequiter.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>
                <ref>¶ Aristotelis pollyticorum: lib. 6. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e174">Multi
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>magis appetunt lucrum quam honorem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>
               <ref>¶ Iesus filius sirach. in ecclesiast. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e184">Noli
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>anxius esse in diuitiis iniustis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e190"> <ref>/ 13. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e192">Bo
        <lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>na est substanria cui non est peccatum in conscia. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e198">
               <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>
                <ref>/ 31. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e202">Beatus diues qui inuentus est sine
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>macula.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e209">
               <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>
                <ref>¶ Terentius in adelphis.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e213">Pecuniam in lo
        <lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>co negligere maximum interdum est lucrum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e219">
               <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>
                <ref>¶ Tullius retho. artis noue: li 6. et fi. c. 5.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e223">Due res sunt que possiunt homines ad tur
        <lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>pe compendium promouere: inopia: atque
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>auaritia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
               <ref>¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum: li. 5. c. 13.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e237">Pul
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>chrum est commodum feda neglexisse lucra
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>pecunie.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e245"> <ref>/ Li. 8. e. 20.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e247">Pecunias illas volu
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>mus quibus libra iustitie suffragatur. <!--221.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e257">
               <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>
                <ref>/ Li. 9. e. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e261">Aurum siquidem per bella que
        <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>rere nephas est: per maria periculum: per
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>falsitates opprobrium: in sua vero natura iustitia.
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>Honesta sunt lucra per que nemo leditur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>Bene queritur quod a nullis adhuc dominis
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>abrogatur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e275"> <ref>/ 14. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e277">Commodum debet esse cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>modo. nam si mensuram equalitatis exces
        <lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>serit vim sui nominis non habebt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e286"> <ref>/ 15. e.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e288">Illud tantum vere possiumus lucrum dicere quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>constat diuina iudicia non punire.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e296"> <ref>/ Li. 11
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>e. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e298">Quid acquiri putatur vbi bena conscia per
        <lb ed="#V" n="57" break="no"/>d tur: aut in qua parte possit homo perfice
        <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>re si innocentiam probatus fuerit amisisse.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e308">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
                <ref>/ Li. 12 e. 13.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e312">Ultra omnes crudelitates est
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>diuitem velle fieri de exiguitate mendici.
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>Amentur honesta lucra: horreantur dam
        <lb ed="#V" n="62" break="no"/>nosa compendia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-d1e322">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>
                <ref>¶ Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 46.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d73148-Qd1e326">Est id tur
        <lb ed="#V" n="64" break="no"/>pe lucrum quod detestatur honestas.
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>Ferre solent damna crimine plena lucra. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
